  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Soul Drifter is an atmospheric single-player first-person platformer set in a surreal underwater world.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553930/extras/3c971627b94e901e368b52780d63f371.poster.avif?t=1741250362\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553930/extras/3c971627b94e901e368b52780d63f371.webm?t=1741250362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553930/extras/3c971627b94e901e368b52780d63f371.mp4?t=1741250362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re a fallen angel in an unfamiliar world. Master your skills to save captive souls in this atmospheric adventure.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gravity-Defying Parkour</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soar into heart-pounding parkour runs on courses only possible for someone with wings. Rack up airtime as you glide across vast chasms, dash through obstacles, and flap your wings for a powerful double jump. String together moves and enter a flow state in which you’ll barely need to touch the ground. Just manage your stamina carefully — there’s nothing to catch you if you fall.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553930/extras/3ae562a7eb1351cae18d9d3c9e7a8a3c.poster.avif?t=1741250362\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553930/extras/3ae562a7eb1351cae18d9d3c9e7a8a3c.webm?t=1741250362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553930/extras/3ae562a7eb1351cae18d9d3c9e7a8a3c.mp4?t=1741250362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Master the Machines</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on fast-paced parkour courses that put your new skills to the test. Muster your courage to enter the final challenge of each level — a massive factory that will challenge both your movement accuracy and reaction time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553930/extras/e89bdd44398cc3d740a53b84215c1649.poster.avif?t=1741250362\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553930/extras/e89bdd44398cc3d740a53b84215c1649.webm?t=1741250362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553930/extras/e89bdd44398cc3d740a53b84215c1649.mp4?t=1741250362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore Strange Landscapes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a surreal, unfamiliar world. Encounter wide open underwater vistas, narrow factory corridors, and towering structures meant to communicate with the gods. Why are other souls kept imprisoned here — and what did their captors intend to do with them?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553930/extras/a853dd1b95cc2f4c94343a10c91755dd.poster.avif?t=1741250362\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553930/extras/a853dd1b95cc2f4c94343a10c91755dd.webm?t=1741250362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553930/extras/a853dd1b95cc2f4c94343a10c91755dd.mp4?t=1741250362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Glide through the air by mastering the stamina system</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Activate special moves like dashes and double jumps</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore levels in a great variety of different biomes, from natural vistas to dangerous factories</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect hidden data tablets to learn more about the strange world you've landed in</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat difficult \"boss\" levels at the end of each area to save your friends</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Soul Drifter is an atmospheric single-player first-person platformer set in a surreal underwater world.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553930/extras/3c971627b94e901e368b52780d63f371.poster.avif?t=1741250362\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553930/extras/3c971627b94e901e368b52780d63f371.webm?t=1741250362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553930/extras/3c971627b94e901e368b52780d63f371.mp4?t=1741250362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re a fallen angel in an unfamiliar world. Master your skills to save captive souls in this atmospheric adventure.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gravity-Defying Parkour</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soar into heart-pounding parkour runs on courses only possible for someone with wings. Rack up airtime as you glide across vast chasms, dash through obstacles, and flap your wings for a powerful double jump. String together moves and enter a flow state in which you’ll barely need to touch the ground. Just manage your stamina carefully — there’s nothing to catch you if you fall.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553930/extras/3ae562a7eb1351cae18d9d3c9e7a8a3c.poster.avif?t=1741250362\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553930/extras/3ae562a7eb1351cae18d9d3c9e7a8a3c.webm?t=1741250362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553930/extras/3ae562a7eb1351cae18d9d3c9e7a8a3c.mp4?t=1741250362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Master the Machines</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on fast-paced parkour courses that put your new skills to the test. Muster your courage to enter the final challenge of each level — a massive factory that will challenge both your movement accuracy and reaction time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553930/extras/e89bdd44398cc3d740a53b84215c1649.poster.avif?t=1741250362\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553930/extras/e89bdd44398cc3d740a53b84215c1649.webm?t=1741250362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553930/extras/e89bdd44398cc3d740a53b84215c1649.mp4?t=1741250362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore Strange Landscapes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a surreal, unfamiliar world. Encounter wide open underwater vistas, narrow factory corridors, and towering structures meant to communicate with the gods. Why are other souls kept imprisoned here — and what did their captors intend to do with them?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553930/extras/a853dd1b95cc2f4c94343a10c91755dd.poster.avif?t=1741250362\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553930/extras/a853dd1b95cc2f4c94343a10c91755dd.webm?t=1741250362\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553930/extras/a853dd1b95cc2f4c94343a10c91755dd.mp4?t=1741250362\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Glide through the air by mastering the stamina system</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Activate special moves like dashes and double jumps</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore levels in a great variety of different biomes, from natural vistas to dangerous factories</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect hidden data tablets to learn more about the strange world you've landed in</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat difficult \"boss\" levels at the end of each area to save your friends</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
